### ─── Health ────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET http://localhost:8000/api/health

###
### Root info (shows resolved paths)
GET http://localhost:8000/

###
### ─── Files ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
### List raw files on disk
GET http://localhost:8000/api/files

###
### List indexed files (RAG ready)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/files/indexed

###
### Refresh index (re-scan all files)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/files/refresh

###
### ─── CDH Catalog ────────────────────────────────────────────
### CDH data sources detected
GET http://localhost:8000/api/cdh/sources

###
### Knowledge articles indexed
GET http://localhost:8000/api/cdh/knowledge-articles

###
### Document templates available
GET http://localhost:8000/api/cdh/templates

###
### ─── Chat — Generic ─────────────────────────────────────────
### Basic file summary
POST http://localhost:8000/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What files are indexed and what do they contain?",
  "stream": false
}

###
### Data analysis query
POST http://localhost:8000/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Which products have the highest profit margin?",
  "stream": false
}

###
### ─── Chat — CDH Knowledge Articles ─────────────────────────
### Arbitration formula
POST http://localhost:8000/api/cdh/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What is the arbitration priority formula in Pega CDH and how does each component work?",
  "stream": false
}

###
### ADM models
POST http://localhost:8000/api/cdh/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What AUC score means an ADM model is failing and what should I do?",
  "stream": false
}

###
### Impact Analyzer
POST http://localhost:8000/api/cdh/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "How does Impact Analyzer work and what scenarios can it simulate?",
  "stream": false
}

###
### Actuals Dataset
POST http://localhost:8000/api/cdh/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "How is the Actuals Dataset constructed and how do I calculate lift?",
  "stream": false
}

###
### Value Finder
POST http://localhost:8000/api/cdh/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What are the Value Finder quadrants and how do I identify underserved customers?",
  "stream": false
}

###
### Knowledge articles only (kb_only=true)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/cdh/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What are the Eligibility and Suitability rules in the Engagement Policy?",
  "stream": false,
  "kb_only": true
}

###
### ─── Document Generation ────────────────────────────────────
### ADM health report
POST http://localhost:8000/api/cdh/generate-document
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Assess ADM model health and identify models needing attention",
  "doc_type": "adm_health_report"
}

###
### NBA performance report
POST http://localhost:8000/api/cdh/generate-document
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Analyse NBA strategy performance across all channels and products",
  "doc_type": "nba_performance_report"
}

###
### KB synthesis report
POST http://localhost:8000/api/cdh/generate-document
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Summarise all CDH arbitration and ADM best practices",
  "doc_type": "kb_synthesis_report"
}

